name: Pukwudgie (Spectral #1)
description: Success! You have found and returned the white, soul orb to it's rightful owner. This is the first of six, Spectral Pukwudgie you will encounter. A Spectral Pukwudgie power's will only allow them to hold one soul orb at a time. There are more power beings in these woods though. For a detailed view of this poor, unfortunate soul that is forever fractured and trapped inside this Pukwudgie's soul orb visit, "The Lost One's #2" (https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/396202). 10/06/2021 Sinner Crypto
